    INode<T>
    public class NAryNode<T extends java.lang.Comparable<T>>
extends SuperNode<T>
implements INode<T>
    Main super class for nodes contained with N-ary derived tress. Contains common functionality that can be used for nodes within different types of N-ary trees.
